cu.explanation_en: Setting the NGAP log level to an invalid value 'invalid' will cause logging initialization failures and prevent proper NGAP protocol handling.

du.explanation_en: Setting do_CSIRS to an invalid value '2' will cause CSI-RS configuration errors and disrupt channel state information processing.
du.explanation_zh: 將 do_CSIRS 設定為無效值 '2' 會導致 CSI-RS 配置錯誤，並干擾通道狀態資訊處理。
